yingyinNormal.en: Well, you'll have to talk to the insurance company.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你得去跟保险公司说。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, don't worry about it, just use your travel insurance. I don't have travel insurance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别担心，你可以用你的旅游保险。我没有旅游保险。

yingyinNormal.en: So, what did you find out about insurance? Oh, yeah. Malpractice insurance is a fortune, but we could bundle it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 保险的事你了解得怎么样了？医疗事故保险要花一大笔钱，但是我们可以把它绑在别的保险上。

yingyinNormal.en: Gosh, love you. Okay, insurance? Oh, yeah, check it. Definitely gonna want some of that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我爱你。保险？哦，打勾，我当然需要保险。

yingyinNormal.en: You don't have insurance? Why? How much is this gonna cost?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你没有保险？要多少钱？

yingyinNormal.en: Blue Cross said my insurance was canceled. The severance package gave me health coverage for up to a year.
yingyinNormal.zh: 蓝十字会告诉我，保险被取消了。解雇金条款里规定了一年的健康保险。

yingyinNormal.en: If you haven't signed up for insurance yet, this is your chance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你还没有注册保险,这就是你的选择。

yingyinNormal.en: And this year insurance premiums for families who are covered through an employer grew at a rate tied for the lowest on record.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今年通过雇主获得医疗保险覆盖家庭的保险费用上涨速度是有史以来最低的。

yingyinNormal.en: That's insurance fraud. Well, all right then, forget it. Why don't we just go home.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是保险欺诈。好吧，算了，我回家。

yingyinNormal.en: We've got resources, lobbyists, worldwide connections and very important, insurance. Insurance is key. All we need now are the super-est superheroes. It needs you three. Come on!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们有资源，说客，还有遍布全球的联系还有非常重要的，保险。保险很关键。现在只缺最厉害的超级英雄了。需要你们三个。来吧！

yingyinNormal.en: For years, they paid about $1,200 a month for their health insurance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 数年来,他们每月都要支付将近$1200的医疗保险。

yingyinNormal.en: 10.9 million new jobs, 10 million more Americans with health insurance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 1090万新的就业岗位，1000多万有着健康保险的国人。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay? Besides, as soon as my insurance kicks in I can get all the free operations I want.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而且只要保险恢复，我就可以动各种免费手术。

yingyinNormal.en: There are no insurance contracts or options for mortgage bonds. The bonds are too stable.
yingyinNormal.zh: 抵押债券没有保险合同或者期权，债券太稳固了。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, but for real, how long do you gotta work here before the health insurance kicks in?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，换个认真的问题，要工作多久才能用医疗保险。

yingyinNormal.en: I tracked it down through insurance records. An old claim that was settled under terms of absolute secrecy.
